ZoneName.SourceString: Ninja Guardian of the Great Forest
ZoneName.LocalizedString: Ninja Guardian of the Great Forest

ZoneDescription.SourceString: Stonewall oversees the great forest, a land rich with magical power and valuable resources. It is said that he only responds to strength. Stand before him in combat and perhaps he will share his bounty.
